name: FUCK YOU AND YOUR PRIUS   100% recycled tote bag
description:
100% recycled canvas tote bag that is MADE IN THE USA by a family owned, and woman operated business. 

RECYCLED COTTON BAG - MADE FROM ECOTEC™
Yarn with Moral Fiber™ & Bottle Bag™ material

This Bag is made from 80% Ecotec™ - a blended cotton yarn produced from the excess fabric of newly made clothing - and 20% Bottle Bag™ material - material made from 100% recycled soda bottles. This unique manufacturing process saves land, energy and water. For the best performance available, 20% of this bag contains 100% recycled soda bottle material.

13"w x 14"h x 3"gusset 25" handles

STAY TUNED. T-SHIRTS ARRIVING IN A COUPLE WEEKS.
